{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Replace council tax for properties worth over \u00a31M with a tax of 0.7%",
        "additional_details": "We believe that by replacing council tax for properties over \u00a31M and taxing the property value by 0.7% per annum would bring them inline with a lot of the poorest property owners. We think this would create fairness.",
        "background": "We call on the Government to tax properties worth more than \u00a31M by 0.7% of their value.",
